{"tid":608570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬會系統疑又故障　觀塘深水埗投注站死機","createTime":"2018-03-28T09:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T09:09:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"84b3db54c886344507a33ac16d842d87ec089dc2","tid":608570,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180328/photo/bkn-20180328164610509-0328_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180328170338\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180328%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180328164610509-0328_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180328170338&h=b2a60322&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港賽馬會繼昨天(27日)出事後，今日下午(28日)投注站投注服務疑再發生系統故障。觀塘開源道投注站投注服務暫停，而深水埗部分投注站亦「跪低」死機。 <br />\n<br />\n馬會昨天已因應情況將六合彩攪珠延至星期四(29日)，今晚快谷將上演8場草地夜賽，暫未知會否受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180328/bkn-20180328164610509-0328_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180328%2Fbkn-20180328164610509-0328_00822_001.html&d=pCGlbbMDkhoO14P0X15fkgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=0d3e023c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180328/bkn-20180328164610509-0328_00822_001.html</a>"}]}